  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK541">
<l>ōrntukaṇ ṇōṭā tiṟaipurin tiyārmāṭṭun </l>
<l> tērntucey kuvatē muṟai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To examine into (the crimes which may be committed), to show no favour (to any one), to desire to act with impartiality towards all, and to inflict (such punishments) as may be wisely resolved on, constitute rectitude.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
